<item>
            <title>[SPARK-24107] ChunkedByteBuffer.writeFully method has not reset the limit value</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-24107</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;ChunkedByteBuffer.writeFully method has not reset the limit value. When &lt;br/&gt;
chunks larger than bufferWriteChunkSize, such as 80*1024*1024 larger than&lt;br/&gt;
config.BUFFER_WRITE_CHUNK_SIZE(64 * 1024 * 1024)&#65292;only while once, will lost 16*1024*1024 byte&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
